bookAuthors: Madame de La Fayette, Terence Cave
Plot: This new translation of The Princesse de Clèves also includes two shorter works also attributed to Mme de Lafayette, The Princesse de Montpensier and The Comtesse de Tende .
Characters: Henri II of France, Jacques de Savoie, duke of Nemours, The Princess of Clèves, Mary, Queen of Scots, Catherine de' Medici
